        <item>
            <title>拉斯維加斯世上最大球型場館 MSG Sphere 落成，覆蓋最高解像度巨型 LED 顯示屏</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/msg-sphere/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=msg-sphere</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/msg-sphere/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 02:27:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MSG Sphere]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[世上最大球型場館]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[沉浸式體驗]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198067</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>全新科技建築 MSG Sphere 於 9 月 29 日在美國拉斯維加斯正式落成。身為世上最大球型場館的 MSG Sphere 採用最先進的技術和設計，將音訊、視訊和感官效果融為一體，為觀眾創造了一種全新的沉浸式體驗。整個 MSG Sphere 總斥資約 23 億美元（約港幣 180 億元）建成。</p><p>MSG Sphere 的外圍由分辨率達 16K x 16K 的巨型 LED 顯示屏組成，是全球分辨率最高的 LED 屏幕。該屏幕可以向上、向下和圍繞觀眾，營造出令人目眩神迷的視覺效果，讓觀眾置身於一個完全沉浸式的環境中，彷彿身臨其境。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.58.44.png"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198072" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.58.44-694x339.png" alt="" width="694" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.58.44-694x339.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.58.44-1280x626.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.58.44-768x375.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.58.44-1536x751.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.58.44.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.28.png"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198073" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.28-694x334.png" alt="" width="694" height="334" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.28-694x334.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.28-1280x616.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.28-768x370.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.28-1536x739.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.28.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.54.png"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198074" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.54-694x355.png" alt="" width="694" height="355" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.54-694x355.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.54-1280x655.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.54-768x393.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.54-1536x786.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-09-08.59.54.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>此外，MSG Sphere 採用了先進的音響技術，包括專為 MSG Sphere 開發的波束成形音響系統。 全新的音響系統能以精確的方式將聲音引導到特定的區域，創造出更逼真的音訊效果。觀眾可以感受到音樂和聲音從四面八方包圍而來，增強了整體的觀賞體驗。</p><p>MSG Sphere 亦引入了多感官的 4D 製作元素，進一步提升了觀眾的參與感。配備次聲波觸覺系統的沉浸式座椅，能透過深層振動讓觀眾身臨其境地感受到雷聲隆隆或摩托車轟鳴的震撼。MSG Sphere 也利用環境特效，如溫度變化、涼風和特定氣味，營造出更逼真的體驗。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_25043"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GUsY8ocXVuk?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>圖片來源：影片截圖<br />
資料來源：<a href="https://www.standard.co.uk/culture/music/msg-sphere-las-vegas-cost-b1111086.html">Evening Standard</a>、<a href="https://liveforlivemusic.com/news/msg-sphere-reveals-first-sphere-experience-postcard-from-earth/">Live For Live Music</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
