            <title>《龍珠：DAIMA》2024 秋季推出，帶來全新冒險故事</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/dragon-ball-daima-will-be-launched-globally-in-the-fall-of-2024-bringing-a-new-adventure-story/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dragon-ball-daima-will-be-launched-globally-in-the-fall-of-2024-bringing-a-new-adventure-story</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/dragon-ball-daima-will-be-launched-globally-in-the-fall-of-2024-bringing-a-new-adventure-story/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蔣納偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 02:22:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[七龍珠]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[七龍珠：DAIMA]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199259</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日舉行的 NYCC 紐約動漫展上，東映動畫公佈了宣佈了一個令粉絲興奮的消息：為紀念龍珠系列 40 週年，將推出全新動畫《龍珠：DAIMA》。在現場，首支前導預告片也得以展示，揭示了一個全新的故事情節，其中悟空和他的夥伴們因受到魔導師的影響而變小，為瞭解決這一事件，他們將踏上通往未知宇宙的冒險之旅。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0000-2.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199369" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0000-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0000-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0000-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0000-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-2.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199370" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0001-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-4.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199371" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0002-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-1.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199372" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/unwire0003-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>《龍珠》的作者鳥山明和「孫悟空」的聲優野澤雅子也在官方發布了訊息。鳥山明表示：「我目前正在製作的龍珠新動畫《龍珠：DAIMA》中的「DAIMA」在日文漢字為「大魔」，在英文中與惡魔的意思相近。本作是一部悟空與夥伴們遭受陰謀，因此受到影響變小的故事。他們將為瞭解決問題前往全新未知的世界展開盛大冒險的故事！能見到小悟空重拾久違的如意棒，這次由我參與本作的故事與大部分設定！帶領大家揭開龍珠世界的奧祕，請享受與之前不同，可愛的戰鬥！」</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-15-上午 10.16.35.jpg"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199373" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-15-上午 10.16.35-460x580.jpg" alt="" width="460" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-15-上午 10.16.35-460x580.jpg 460w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-15-上午 10.16.35-714x900.jpg 714w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-15-上午 10.16.35-768x968.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-15-上午 10.16.35-1218x1536.jpg 1218w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕截圖-2023-10-15-上午 10.16.35.jpg 1269w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 460px" /></a></p><p>而野澤雅子則表示：「《龍珠：DAIMA》的新預告太棒了~！小悟空也太可愛！是怎樣的陰謀導致悟空變成這樣？目前仍然是祕密！有點興奮了呢！請大家多多期待新七龍珠動畫！」</p><p>目前釋出的細節還很少，但據消息指出，本作的時間點將設定在《龍珠 Z》之後與《龍珠，超》之前，作品風格將回歸早期龍珠的不思議大冒險風格，期望回歸龍珠系列的原點。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_99755"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/tkzzoDLrRDM?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=257563">GNN</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
