        <item>
            <title>美國女玩家嫌遊戲角色胸部太細   34DD 也無法重現其傲人身材</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/us-female-gamer-complains-that-video-game-breast-size-too-small/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=us-female-gamer-complains-that-video-game-breast-size-too-small</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/15/us-female-gamer-complains-that-video-game-breast-size-too-small/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sun, 15 Oct 2023 02:13:39 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[遊戲情報]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1198588</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>很多遊戲女角色衣著非常清涼，間中被衞道之士批評身材過份玲瓏浮凸。不過最近外國 Reddit 女網友 <a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/deviantmoth/">@deviantmoth</a> 卻嫌遊戲裏的女性角色胸部不夠大，令她無法創造出與她本人身材相符的角色。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1198610" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-11-164836-694x331.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="331" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-11-164836-694x331.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-11-164836-768x367.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/螢幕擷取畫面-2023-10-11-164836.jpg 817w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>deviantmoth 表示：「我的胸部很大，我也想有個和我相似的遊戲角色，但一直都很困難，因為（在遊戲開發商角度而言）任何大於 DD 的胸部都是『不切實際的』。有時我會和其他遊戲玩家抱怨，但他們就只會覺得我反應過大。」deviantmoth 補充指，美國平均胸部尺寸是 DD，而大部份遊戲中 DD 已經是最大的尺寸。</p><p>有網民回覆指，開發者或擔心被批評物化女性，所以限制女角胸部大細。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="reddit-embed-bq" style="height:316px" ><p><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/gaming/comments/16uslei/why_is_there_such_a_stigma_of_large_boobs_in/">Why is there such a stigma of large boobs in video games?</a><br /> by<a href="https://www.reddit.com/user/deviantmoth/">u/deviantmoth</a> in<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/gaming/">gaming</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://embed.reddit.com/widgets.js" charset="UTF-8"></script></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/gaming/comments/16uslei/why_is_there_such_a_stigma_of_large_boobs_in/?rdt=35123">Reddit</a>、<a href="https://hot.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/game/1388723.htm">cnBeta</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
